title: BRIEF-Net Insight wins 2 mln EUR order in Switzerland
text:
Sept 11 Net Insight Ab
* Net insight ab : net insight signs significant contract with swisscom broadcast for digital terrestrial tv network
* Net insight ab says value of deliveries of this project under contract is estimated to around eur 2 million Further company coverage: (Reporting By Anna Ringstrom)
